Popular Nigerian cross dresser, Idris Okuneye popularly known as Bobrisky has suffered disgrace in the hands of Nigerians in faraway Dubai. The cross dresser was verbally attacked by Nigerians who do not like his way of life. In a video that surfaced online, some Nigerians in Dubai could be seen raining curses on him and his grandmother. Bobrisky wore a red flowing gown and was in the midst of two beautiful women as he paid no attention to the men cursing and recording him. Recall that few days ago, Bobrisky shared a photo of himself seated and sipping champagne in the first class section of a plane heading to Dubai. He captioned the photo: “Bobrisky flew first class again this week… I only fly first class, let me see if they will refuse me entry” Watch video below: Source